  "key": "STITCH-1234",
  "renderedFields": {
    "description": "<p>As a user, I want to be able to reset my password via email so that I can regain access to my account if I forget my credentials.</p>\n<h3>Acceptance Criteria</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>User receives a password reset email within 60 seconds</li>\n<li>Reset link expires after 24 hours</li>\n<li>User cannot reuse last 5 passwords</li>\n<li>Failed reset attempts are logged for security audit</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Technical Notes</h3>\n<p>Use the existing email service. Token should be a signed JWT with 24h expiry. Store password history hashes in the <code>password_history</code> table.</p>",
    "comment": {
      "comments": []
    },
